sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>openshift-ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant HTTPRoute as HTTPRoute<br/>Path: /mlflow/*
    participant MLflowSvc as MLflow Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflowPod as MLflow Pod<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3<br/>kubernetes-auth
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS1.2+

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 1: User Access to MLflow via Gateway

    User->>Gateway: HTTPS Request /mlflow/api/2.0/*<br/>Bearer Token (K8s)
    Gateway->>HTTPRoute: Route based on path prefix
    HTTPRoute->>MLflowSvc: Forward to backend<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    MLflowSvc->>MLflowPod: Forward to pod<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: self_subject_access_review<br/>ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Authorization Result

    alt Authorized
        MLflowPod-->>User: MLflow API Response<br/>JSON
    else Unauthorized
        MLflowPod-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: MLflow Artifact Storage (S3)

    User->>MLflowPod: Log Artifact<br/>POST /api/2.0/mlflow/artifacts<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: Validate Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Valid
    MLflowPod->>S3: PUT Object<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS IAM/Access Keys
    S3-->>MLflowPod: Stored
    MLflowPod-->>User: Artifact Logged

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 3: MLflow Metadata Storage (PostgreSQL)

    User->>MLflowPod: Create Experiment<br/>POST /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/create<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: Validate Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Valid
    MLflowPod->>PostgreSQL: INSERT INTO experiments<br/>5432/TCP TLS<br/>Username/Password
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflowPod: Inserted
    MLflowPod-->>User: Experiment Created

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>Controller Pod
    participant HelmChart as Embedded Helm Chart

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>MLflow CR Created/Updated
    Operator->>HelmChart: Render Templates<br/>Local filesystem
    HelmChart-->>Operator: Manifests (YAML)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Resources<br/>Deployment, Service, HTTPRoute, etc.<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources Created

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 5: Prometheus Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant OpMetrics as Operator Metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Prometheus->>OpMetrics: GET /metrics<br/>Bearer Token<br/>TLS1.2+
    OpMetrics-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics
